attributionInfo.brokerName: Keller Williams Realty Boston-Metro | Back Bay

description: Here is your Opportunity to own this Classic, well- maintained Two Family Home in the Heart of South Boston with 2184 sq ft of living area. Each spacious unit has two bedrooms, a bonus room, one bathroom, a living room with Victorian sash style windows and kitchen. Hardwood floors gleam throughout and stylish French doors add historic charm to this property built in 1900. The full basement has a walk-out to the fenced-in backyard, windows, a workshop bench and ample room for storage. Incredible location! A true commuter's delight to Downtown Boston and Seaport District. Close proximity to major highways, airport, beach, Castle Island, the Seaport, and shops on Broadway. Bring your design ideas to make your own! Offer Deadline: 2/10 at noon. All offers must be subject to the Probate Court issuing a License to Sell for the offered price.
